query: 每个洲有多少个国家？列出大洲ID、大洲名称和国家数目。
pred: SELECT c.ContId, c.Continent, COUNT(co.CountryId) AS NumberOfCountries FROM continents c JOIN countries co ON c.ContId = co.Continent GROUP BY c.ContId, c.Continent;
ground_truth: SELECT T1.ContId ,  T1.Continent ,  count(*) FROM CONTINENTS AS T1 JOIN COUNTRIES AS T2 ON T1.ContId  =  T2.Continent GROUP BY T1.ContId;

query: 对于每个大洲，列出它的ID、名字和它有多少个国家？
pred: SELECT continents.ContId, continents.Continent, COUNT(countries.CountryId) AS NumberOfCountries FROM continents LEFT JOIN countries ON continents.ContId = countries.Continent GROUP BY continents.ContId, continents.Continent;
ground_truth: SELECT T1.ContId ,  T1.Continent ,  count(*) FROM CONTINENTS AS T1 JOIN COUNTRIES AS T2 ON T1.ContId  =  T2.Continent GROUP BY T1.ContId;

query: 每个汽车制造商生产多少种型号的汽车？列出制造商姓名，ID和号码。
pred: SELECT cm.Maker, cm.Id, COUNT(ml.ModelId) AS NumberOfModels FROM car_makers cm LEFT JOIN model_list ml ON cm.Id = ml.Maker GROUP BY cm.Id, cm.Maker;
ground_truth: SELECT T1.FullName ,  T1.Id ,  count(*) FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker GROUP BY T1.Id;

query: 每个汽车制造商的全名，ID以及生产多少种型号的汽车？
pred: SELECT car_makers.FullName, car_makers.Id, COUNT(model_list.ModelId) AS NumberOfModels FROM car_makers LEFT JOIN model_list ON car_makers.Id = model_list.Maker GROUP BY car_makers.Id, car_makers.FullName;
ground_truth: SELECT T1.FullName ,  T1.Id ,  count(*) FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker GROUP BY T1.Id;

pred: SELECT c.Make FROM cars_data AS cd JOIN car_names AS c ON cd.Id = c.MakeId WHERE CAST(cd.Horsepower AS INTEGER) = (SELECT MIN(CAST(Horsepower AS INTEGER)) FROM cars_data) LIMIT 1;
ground_truth: SELECT T1.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id ORDER BY T2.horsepower ASC LIMIT 1;

query: 最小马力的汽车的型号是什么？
pred: SELECT model_list.Model FROM cars_data JOIN car_names ON cars_data.Id = car_names.MakeId JOIN model_list ON car_names.Model = model_list.Model WHERE CAST(cars_data.Horsepower AS INTEGER) = (SELECT MIN(CAST(Horsepower AS INTEGER)) FROM cars_data);
ground_truth: SELECT T1.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id ORDER BY T2.horsepower ASC LIMIT 1;

query: 找出重量低于平均重量的汽车的型号。
pred: SELECT DISTINCT car_names.Model FROM cars_data JOIN car_names ON cars_data.Id = car_names.MakeId WHERE cars_data.Weight < (SELECT AVG(Weight) FROM cars_data);
ground_truth: SELECT T1.model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id WHERE T2.Weight  <  (SELECT avg(Weight) FROM CARS_DATA)

query: 重量小于平均值的汽车的型号是什么？
pred: SELECT DISTINCT model_list.Model FROM cars_data JOIN car_names ON cars_data.Id = car_names.MakeId JOIN model_list ON car_names.Model = model_list.Model WHERE cars_data.Weight < (SELECT AVG(Weight) FROM cars_data);
ground_truth: SELECT T1.model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN CARS_DATA AS T2 ON T1.MakeId  =  T2.Id WHERE T2.Weight  <  (SELECT avg(Weight) FROM CARS_DATA)

query: 找出“1970”年生产汽车的制造商的名字。
pred: SELECT DISTINCT car_makers.Maker FROM car_makers JOIN model_list ON car_makers.Id = model_list.Maker JOIN car_names ON model_list.Model = car_names.Model JOIN cars_data ON car_names.MakeId = cars_data.Id WHERE cars_data.Year = 1970;
ground_truth: SELECT DISTINCT T1.Maker FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T3 ON T2.model  =  T3.model JOIN CARS_DATA AS T4 ON T3.MakeId  =  T4.id WHERE T4.year  =  '1970';
